msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "In Weex, we use the *mustache* syntax `{{...}}` to bind data in `<template>` which are defined in `<script>`. Once data and template is bound, the data changes will influence the corresponding template content immediately and automatically.\n"
msgstr "在 weex 中，我们使用 *mustache* 的语法 `{{...}}`，来绑定 `<template>` 模板 和 `<script>` 脚本 中的数据。 一旦 数据-模板 绑定了，脚本中数据的修改，会在模板的内容中实时生效。\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "Binding data path"
msgstr "如何绑定数据？"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```html\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <container>\n"
"    <text style=\"font-size: {{size}}\">{{title}}</text>\n"
"  </container>\n"
"</template>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:25
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<script>\n"
"  module.exports = {\n"
"    data: {\n"
"      size: 48,\n"
"      title: 'Alibaba Weex Team'\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"</script>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:27
msgid ""
"The code above will bind the `title` and `size` data field to `template`."
msgstr "上面的代码会把 `title` 和 `size` 绑定到模板上。"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:29
msgid ""
"We can also use `.` syntax to bind cascading data structure. Let's look at "
"the following code snippet:"
msgstr ""
"我们也可以用 `.` 语法来绑定多层的数据结构。让我们来看看下面的代码片段："

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```html\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <container>\n"
"    <text style=\"font-size: {{title.size}}\">{{title.value}}</text>\n"
"  </container>\n"
"</template>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:48
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<script>\n"
"  module.exports = {\n"
"    data: {\n"
"      title: {\n"
"        size: 48,\n"
"        value: 'Alibaba Weex Team'\n"
"      }\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"</script>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "In-template expression"
msgstr "模板表达式"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:52
msgid "Inside data bindings, Weex supports simply javascript expressions, e.g."
msgstr "在数据绑定中， weex 支持简单的 JavaScript 表达式计算，例如："

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:59
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```html\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <container style=\"flex-direction: row;\">\n"
"    <text>{{firstName + ' ' + lastName}}</text>\n"
"  </container>\n"
"</template>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:69
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<script>\n"
"  module.exports = {\n"
"    data: {\n"
"      firstName: 'John',\n"
"      lastName: 'Smith'\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"</script>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:71
msgid "The expression will be evaluated in the data scope of current context."
msgstr "该表达式将在当前上下文内进行求值。"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:73
#, no-wrap
msgid "**NOTE: EACH BINDING CAN ONLY CONTAIN ONE SINGLE EXPRESSION**\n"
msgstr "*** 注意：每一个绑定只能包含一个表达式 **"

#. type: Title ##
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "Computed Properties "
msgstr "求值属性"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:76
#, no-wrap
msgid "<span class=\"weex-version\">0.5</span>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:78
msgid ""
"According to simple operations, in-template expressions are very convenient. "
"But if you want to put more logic into the template, you should use a "
"computed property."
msgstr ""
"简单的计算，用模板表达式非常方便。但是，如果你想把更多的逻辑放在模板中，你应"
"该使用一个求值属性。"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:87
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"e.g.\n"
"```html\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <container style=\"flex-direction: row;\">\n"
"    <text>{{fullName}}</text>\n"
"    <text onclick=\"changeName\"></text>\n"
"  </container>\n"
"</template>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:99
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<script>\n"
"  module.exports = {\n"
"    data: {\n"
"      firstName: 'John',\n"
"      lastName: 'Smith'\n"
"    },\n"
"    computed: {\n"
"      fullName: {\n"
"        get: function() {\n"
"          return this.firstName + ' ' + this.lastName\n"
"        },\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:115
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"        set: function(v) {\n"
"          var s = v.split(' ')\n"
"          this.firstName = s[0]\n"
"          this.lastName = s[1]\n"
"        }\n"
"      }\n"
"    },\n"
"    methods: {\n"
"      changeName: function() {\n"
"        this.fullName = 'Terry King'\n"
"      }\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"</script>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:117
msgid ""
"Here we have declared a computed property fullName. The function we provided "
"will be used as the getter function for concating firstName and lastName."
msgstr ""
"在这里，我们声明了一个求值属性 fullName 。 同时，定义了求值函数来连接 "
"firstName和 lastName 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:119
msgid ""
"Otherwise when you call `changeName` after click, the setter will be invoked "
"and this.firstName and this.lastName will be updated accordingly."
msgstr ""
"同时，当你点击调用 `changeName` 后， 会通过 set 函数来赋值，this.firstname "
"和 this.lastname 会相应的更新。"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:121
#, no-wrap
msgid "**NOTE: `data` and `methods` can't have duplicated fields. 'Cause in the execution context -- `this`, we can access both of them.**\n"
msgstr "***注意：`data` 和 `methods` 的字段不能重复。 因为在执行上下文中 - 通过 `this` ，我们可以同时访问这两者 **。 \n"

#. type: Title ##
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:122
#, no-wrap
msgid "Usage of some special attributes in Data-Binding"
msgstr "特殊属性的数据绑定"

#. type: Title ###
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:124
#, no-wrap
msgid "Styles: `style` or `class`"
msgstr "样式 ：`style` 或 `class`"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:127
msgid "the style of a component can be bind using the `style` attribute:"
msgstr "一个组件的样式可以通过 `style` 属性来绑定："

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:133
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```html\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <text style=\"font-size: {{size}}; color: {{color}}; ...\">...</text>\n"
"</template>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:135
msgid ""
"while style can also get bound with `class` attribute, multiple classnames "
"can be split by spaces:"
msgstr "样式也能够通过 `class` 属性实现绑定，多个 classname 之间通过空格分隔:"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:144
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```html\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <container>\n"
"    <text class=\"{{size}}\"></text>\n"
"    <text class=\"title {{status}}\"></text>\n"
"  </container>\n"
"</template>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:146
msgid ""
"here if `{{size}}` and `{{status}}` have empty value, then only `class="
"\"title\"` will be rendered."
msgstr ""
"在上面的代码中如果 `{{size}}` 和 `{{status}}` 是空值, 就只有 `class=\"title"
"\"` 会被渲染。"

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:148
msgid "[See more about style and class](./style-n-class.md)"
msgstr "[参见 样式和类](./style-n-class.md)"

#. type: Title ###
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:149
#, no-wrap
msgid "Event Handler: `on...`"
msgstr "事件响应：`on...`"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:152
msgid ""
"The event handler is an attribute which name has a prefix `on...`. The other "
"part of attribute name is event type and the value is event handler name. We "
"don't need to add mustache around the method name or add parentheses to call "
"it."
msgstr ""
"事件响应是一个以 `on` 为前缀的属性 。 属性名称的另一部分是事件类型，值是响应"
"事件的函数名。调用时，我们无需添加 mustache 语法中的括号。"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:157
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```html\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <text onclick=\"toggle\">Toggle</text>\n"
"</template>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:168
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<script>\n"
"  module.exports = {\n"
"    methods: {\n"
"      toggle: function () {\n"
"        // todo\n"
"      }\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"</script>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:169
#, no-wrap
msgid "`if` & `repeat`"
msgstr " `if` & `repeat`"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:172
msgid ""
"`if` attribute can control the display of a component by a truthy/falsy "
"value."
msgstr " `if` 属性可以通过值的真/假，来控制一个组件是否显示。"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:180
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```html\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <container style=\"flex-direction: column;\">\n"
"    <text onclick=\"toggle\">Toggle</text>\n"
"    <image src=\"...\" if=\"{{shown}}\"></image>\n"
"  </container>\n"
"</template>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:194
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<script>\n"
"  module.exports = {\n"
"    data: {\n"
"      shown: true\n"
"    },\n"
"    methods: {\n"
"      toggle: function () {\n"
"        this.shown = !this.shown\n"
"      }\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"</script>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:196
msgid "We can also use `repeat` attribute to generate a list."
msgstr "`repeat` 属性可以用于生成一个列表。 "

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:198
#, no-wrap
msgid "**NOTE: When you want to mutate an array in `data`. Something limitations existing below:**\n"
msgstr "**注意：想改变在 `data` 数组，有些限制：** ???\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:200
msgid ""
"When you directly set an item with the index (`vm.items[0] = {};`), it won't "
"trigger view update. So we have a prototype methods: `$set(index, item)`."
msgstr ""
"当你通过索引位置直接设置一个条目 (`vm.items[0] = {};`) , 不会触发模板视图的更"
"新。所以，更新数组用这个函数 : `$set(index, item)`。 "

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:205
msgid ""
"``` // same as `example1.items[0] = ...` but triggers view update example1."
"items.$set(0, { childMsg: 'Changed!'})  ```"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:207
msgid ""
"When you modify the length of the Array (`vm.items.length = 0`), it won't "
"trigger view update too. We recommend you just replace `items` with an empty "
"array instead."
msgstr ""
"当你修改数组的长度(`vm.items.length = 0`), 不会触发模板视图的更新。 你可以直"
"接给 `items` 赋值空数组。"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:212
msgid ""
"``` // same as `example2.items.length = 0` but triggers view update example2."
"items = [] ```"
msgstr ""

